"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-06-07-jaaa-clarifies-relay-training-guideline-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Jamaicanathletes who are selected for the men's and women's 4x100m and 4x400m pools and fail to show up for practice could be excluded from competing in the relays at this summer's Paris Olympic Games, the Jamaica Athletics Administrative Association (JAAA) has moved to clarify.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 279, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 206, \"end\": 250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Athletics_Administrative_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jamaica Athletics Administrative Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Athletics_Administrative_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Athletics_Administrative_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jamaicanathletes\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 16}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's and women's 4x100m\", \"from\": 38, \"to\": 66}, {\"ngram\": \"pools\", \"from\": 78, \"to\": 83}, {\"ngram\": \"practice\", \"from\": 108, \"to\": 116}, {\"ngram\": \"the relays\", \"from\": 153, \"to\": 163}, {\"ngram\": \"this summer's Paris Olympic Games\", \"from\": 167, \"to\": 200}, {\"ngram\": \"JAAA\", \"from\": 252, \"to\": 256}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is a condition for selection that the athletes selected for the relay pool should make themselves available when required for relay practice.\", \"from\": 281, \"to\": 426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a condition\", \"from\": 288, \"to\": 299}, {\"ngram\": \"selection\", \"from\": 304, \"to\": 313}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 331}, {\"ngram\": \"the relay pool\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 359}, {\"ngram\": \"relay practice\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes who fail to make themselves available may not be allowed to participate in the competition,\\\" stated a document which the JAAA circulated among shareholders.\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 592, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 557, \"end\": 561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Athletics_Administrative_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"JAAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Athletics_Administrative_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Athletics_Administrative_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 435}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 526}, {\"ngram\": \"a document\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"shareholders\", \"from\": 579, \"to\": 591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lincoln Eatmon, chairman of the selection committee, told theJamaica Observerthis week that the \\\"competition\\\" referred to in the document was the relays and not the Olympic Games as a whole.\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 784, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 594, \"end\": 601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abraham_Lincoln\", \"score\": 0.9999918465742186, \"rank\": 8.15349234118543e-06, \"text\": \"Lincoln\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abraham_Lincoln\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abraham_Lincoln\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"chairman\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 618}, {\"ngram\": \"the selection committee\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 645}, {\"ngram\": \"theJamaica\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 662}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"competition\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 702}, {\"ngram\": \"the document\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 731}, {\"ngram\": \"the relays\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 746}, {\"ngram\": \"not the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 772}, {\"ngram\": \"a whole\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 783}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The requirement to make themselves available for relay practice is a JAAA requirement,\\\" he pointed out, while adding that the requirement is \\\